## Deferred (do not implement as if shipped)

Plugins, Git automation, Terminology/Structure validators, multi-language `.lilt/<lang>/`,
AST-node identity Phase 2, HTTP/TUI/web UI, multi-format (Markdown/AsciiDoc).
See [appendix-deferred](docs/architecture/appendix-deferred.md).

## Toolchain and validation (same as CI)

- Python 3.13+; package management with `uv` only.
- Prefer `make ci` as the non-mutating gate matching GitHub Actions.
- Equivalent: `uv run ruff format --check .`, `uv run ruff check .`, `uv run mypy src/ tests/`, `uv run pytest`.

## Documentation language

- Project docs, AI context files (rules, skills), and code comments/docstrings MUST be **English**.
- Conversations with the user may be in any language; generated artifacts are not.
- This is a Typer CLI, not a web framework — ignore FastAPI/Django suggestions unless asked.
